(
    [missionStatus] => 1
    [missionStatusHidden] => 1
    [web_content_1] => About Circuit Brilliance
    [web_content_2] => <div><div>Circuit Brilliance is a specialist power electronics design consultancy founded in July 2024. We do one thing — power electronics PCB design — and we do it properly. EV chargers, renewable energy inverters, battery management systems, and high-power converters are not a side service here. They are the only service.</div><div>Every Circuit Brilliance engagement is backed by six proprietary analytical frameworks — built from 18 years of hands-on domain experience. What this means for you: your design is evaluated for failure risk before a single trace is routed. Every watt of loss is accounted for before the BOM is finalised. Compliance gaps are identified at the schematic stage, not at the test lab. Thermal risks are mapped before the layout begins. These are not optional reviews — they are how Circuit Brilliance works on every project, regardless of size or domain.</div><div>Circuit Brilliance also works as a full power electronics product development partner. If you are developing a power electronics product from the ground up — across EV, BMS, renewable energy, or power conversion — we can work with you from the initial block diagram through topology selection, simulation, schematic capture, PCB layout, and complete design documentation. The capability is here. The domain depth is here. And the structured methodology to take a product from concept to production-ready design is built into everything we do.</div></div>    
    [web_content_id] => 7
    [for] => edit
)

