    [web_content_1] => More than projects. A design hub
    [web_content_2] => Circuit Brilliance is building towards something larger than a project-by-project consultancy. The technical blog, the case study portfolio, the design frameworks, and the growing domain knowledge base are all pointing towards a power electronics design hub that the EV and renewable energy engineering community can genuinely rely on. The world needs more good power electronics design. We intend to help.
    [web_content_3] => Power Electronics Research Institute
    [web_content_4] => PERI — the Power Electronics Research Institute — is Circuit Brilliance's academic wing, currently being established to advance power electronics knowledge through structured research, technical publication, and collaboration with university research groups. Because good engineering deserves to be understood, shared, and built upon.
